#ROOMS
#13201
Gathering your Bearings~
You've been wandering through the lands for some time now,
travelling over mountains and through forests, passing miles
upon miles of plains, arriving to this place.  You don't
know quite what land this is, and who may rule it.  You're
not even sure if you will meet anyone along your way in this
foreign place..  Only that adventure is your goal, and what may
cross along your path is yet for you to see.
From where you stand here on this ledge you're looking down
upon a dark area of land, a land that looks minorly flooded
best to what you can tell.  There's no point in even trying to turn
back now, you must venture on, and you must begin that by making
your way down a relatively steep cliffside here.
~
~
