#13202
A Wetlands~
You're standing near a cliffside, looking up upon which you
have just slidden down without too much trouble, yet would
be near impossible to make your way back up.
The earth is mushed with water, and thick vegetation grows
all around, blocking your way in a great many directions.
The sky above is dim even during daytime in this land,
thank goodness you made sure to pack some torches when you
left...  though that seems like ages ago.
~
