The Marsh~
A disturbing feeling runs through your body as you wander
around the wetlands to the menacing sky looming above,
cloaking the land in a shade as far as you can see.  Full
green and florishing plants raise out from below the slight
cover of water across the ground, and wrap around even more
plants, creating annoying blockades to some directions you
might otherwise travel...  Cutting through wouldn't be an
