#13215
The Marsh~
Your surroudings seem to be pretty desolate, brown opague water
covers the ground, too muddy to see through.  Long blades of
grass and an occasionally more evolved plant with leaves poke
just slightly up from underneath, and a few incredibly annoying
insects buzz your face, taunting you most likely to try to do
something about it...you clasp your hand tighter around your
weapon...
