#13216
The Marsh~
The daytime isn't much different from nighttime, with a
seemingly permanent shadow cast over this land, making it look
all the more gloomy, and a chilly breeze often runs across the
land at a high speed, making things all the more unpleasent.
Hopefully you'll pass through this geographic region quickly
and get to something better on the other side.
To your north is the cliffside to higher land, but there is no
way to get up here nor anywhere else you can find.
~
The nighttime isn't much different from daytime here, though
still visually darker since there is no sun in the sky.  The
wetlands seem gloomy and threatening, though signs of living
anything are nowhere to be found here.
Hopefully you'll pass through this geographic region quickly
and get to something better on the other side.
~
